Class CashRegisterConsoleUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • cashregister.ui.CashRegisterConsoleUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICashRegisterUI
    public class CashRegisterConsoleUI
extends Object
implements ICashRegisterUI
    Provides an implementation for a console based user interface for an ICashRegister. It implements the ICashRegisterUI interface and provides a simple output to System.out (console).
